text: WBFK (91.1 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Hiseville, Kentucky. The station is owned by Bethel Fellowship, Inc., and airs a Christian radio format. The station was assigned the WBFK call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on August 14, 2012. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * FCC Public Inspection File for WBFK * BFK Category:Radio stations established in 2012 Category:2012 establishments in Kentucky BFK Category:Barren County, Kentucky
